executive vice presidents at Backer Spielvogel Bates, a unit
of Saatchi &amp; Saatchi. . . . Randall D. Schroeder was named
executive vice president and management director of media at
Saatchi's Campbell-Mithun-Esty, Detroit.
                                                                                                       

   KOREY KAY: American Safety Razor Co., Staunton, Va., named
Korey, Kay &amp; Partners, New York, to handle its $4 million ad
account. Korey Kay will create ads for American Safety brands
Personna, Flicker and LegMate.
                                                                                                       

